obj_root_law_sections_1:
  sectionId (67691)
  sectionNo (1)
  orderNo 1
  title `Ghatwals of Beerbhoom to have the same right of granting leases as is allowed to other proprietors of lands.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_1_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_1_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_5_5_00088_1859-05_1660728881582&sectionId=67691&sectionno=1&orderno=1&orgactid=AC_CEN_5_5_00088_1859-05_1660728881582
obj_root_law_sections_1_content:
  string
  line `Ghatwals holding lands in the District of Beerbhoom under the provisions of the`
  line `aforesaid Regulation, shall have the same power of granting leases for any period which they may deem`
  line `most conducive to the improvement of their tenures, as is allowed by law to the proprietors of other lands.`
  line
  line `Proviso. ----Provided that no lease of Ghatwalee lands for any period extending beyond the life-time or`
  line `incumbency of the grantor of the lease shall be valid and binding on the successors of the grantor, unless`
  line `the same shall be granted for the working of mines, or for the clearing of jungle, or for the erection of`
  line `dwelling houses or manufactories, or for tanks, canals, and similar works; and shall be approved by the`
  line `Commissioner of the Division, such approval being certified by an endorsement on the lease under the`
  line `signature of the Commissioner`
obj_root_law_sections_1_footnotes:
  string
  line
obj_root_law_sections_2:
  sectionId (67692)
  sectionNo (2)
  orderNo 2
  title `Court of Wards and Revenue authorities to have the like power in certain causes.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_2_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_2_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_5_5_00088_1859-05_1660728881582&sectionId=67692&sectionno=2&orderno=2&orgactid=AC_CEN_5_5_00088_1859-05_1660728881582
obj_root_law_sections_2_content:
  string
  line `If any of`
  line `the said Ghatwalee lands be at any time under the superintendence of the Court of Wards, or otherwise`
  line `subject to the direct control of the Officers of Government, it shall be lawful for the Court of Wards or the`
  line `Commissioner to grant leases for any such purpose as aforesaid; and every lease so granted shall be valid`
  line `and binding on all future possessors of the said lands, anything in the existing law to the contrary`
  line notwithstanding.
obj_root_law_sections_2_footnotes:
  string
  line
